  <excursions><![CDATA[<h3>Lake Garda Promotion Card included for all Inghams guests</h3>
<p>The <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.visitlimonesulgarda.com/images/pdf/promotion-card-2022.pdf" target="_blank">Garda Promotion Card</a> gives you discounts on various local cultural sites such as museums, waterparks and castles. You can even get discounts on bike rentals if you fancy a day cycling by the lakeside. The card can be used over three days and you can get it for free from any of our hotels.</p>]]></excursions>
