  <insidersGuide><![CDATA[<p style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">Good to know</p>
<p><strong>Walking trails:</strong> 175km of walking trails</p>
<p><strong>Terrain:</strong> Varied terrain from mountain climbs to a flat walk along the lakeside </p>
<p><strong>Best time to go:</strong> June to October. It can get quite warm in July and August so cool off with a dip in the lake </p>
<p><strong>Best for:</strong> All walking abilities, nature and sightseeing</p>
<p><strong>Fly into:</strong> Verona (approx. 2 hours)</p>
<p><strong>Fly from:</strong> London Gatwick, Manchester, Bristol, Edinburgh, Glasgow, Birmingham, Newcastle, Leeds Bradford, East Midlands</p>
<p><strong>Transfer time:</strong> approx. 2 hours 15 mins by coach</p>
<p><strong>Resort card:</strong> Free Garda Promotion Card</p>
<p><strong>24/7 Support and advice: </strong>In person or over the phone from our local resort team based in Limone</p>
<p><strong>Inghams Guided Walks included</strong></p>]]></insidersGuide>
