  <walkingGeneralDescription><![CDATA[<p><span>On an Inghams walking holiday, you have the freedom to explore the area at your own pace. <span>Make each day a new adventure, with as much or as little walking as you like.</span></span></p>
<h3>Why we love walking in Limone</h3>
<p>Who knew that Lake Garda had so many fantastic opportunities for walking. Come to Limone and experience it in a new way, heading into the surrounding mountains and exploring vineyards and trails with stunning lake views. Walking here gives you a completely different perspective of the surrounding area and means you can get to know the hidden gems of this popular resort.</p>
<h3>Guided walks</h3>
<p>Don't forget, you have the option to join two included Inghams guided walks per week, with a local, professional guide. Get to know our favourite walking trails with insider knowledge and the company of other guests. Pre-booking is essential - <span>check out the Guided Walks section below for more information.</span></p>]]></walkingGeneralDescription>
